As frases utilizadas para os testes (sem incluir a descrição "Positivo"/"Negativo"/"Neutro").

Positivo: "I was thoroughly impressed by the new smartphone’s vibrant display and blazing-fast performance, making every interaction a delight."
Negativo: "The hotel room felt cramped and outdated, with a lingering musty odor that made the entire stay uncomfortable."
Neutro: "The restaurant offers a standard dining experience, with a menu that meets expectations but doesn't particularly stand out."
Positivo: "I absolutely loved the sleek design and intuitive interface of the smartwatch—it’s become an essential part of my daily routine."
Negativo: "The laptop consistently disappointed me with its frequent overheating and short battery life, which hampered my productivity."
Neutro: "The new tablet meets standard expectations for everyday tasks with reliable performance, but it lacks any unique standout features."
